cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper deals with line segment detection in images, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm uses probabilistic methods and dynamic programming, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The evaluation methodology developed in the paper also involves measuring the accuracy of the algorithm, which is a common task in graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO).
